Package: mtmiller-base
Architecture: all
Depends: bash-completion,
         byobu,
         debian-goodies,
         lsb,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: commonly installed Debian system packages
 This package installs mtmiller's base Debian system configuration.
 .
 This is a dependency package that installs common system packages.

